reviews.comment:
As always, mdakash5 did a flawless job; he's 100% reliable, incredibly fast at delivering great results and his designs have translated extremely well to alternate media (we used two of his designs as challenge coins to promote a new line of business -- they were phenomenally popular!)

I recommend mdakash5 wholeheartedly and without reservation.

What I like the most about mdakash5 is that the communication is right away. They do not take hours to respond. Once the job is requested I feel like the response time for finished product was expeditious. I definitely recommend this seller. Great experience. Thank you.

Absolute pleasure to work with and was extremely fast at getting my project done. A true professional and would HIGHLY recommend to anyone and everyone. Great communication and overall experience. The final design was even better than what I could dream up.

Ali was quick and efficient with his logo editing service. I had a logo that was hand drawn so it needed to be finalized and Ali created 3 logos to choose from. I went with 1 logo from the first pass. I was pleased with the quality.

Was an excellent experience working with Ali Redesign. He was able to recreate high-quality versions of our existing logo in several formats, within 24 hours.

Would definitely use him again and would recommend others to do the same if you're looking for high-quality work with a quick turnaround.
